==Demographics==
As of the 2020 Census, the Suncrest CDP had a population of 5,413 residents across 1,922 households.<ref name="QuickFacts" /> Estimates by the Census Bureau as of July 1, 2021 show that 94.6% of the population is white alone, 0.0% Black alone, 1.2% American Indian or Alaska Native alone, 1.0% Asian alone, 0.0% Native Hawaiian or Pacific Islander alone, 3.2% two or more races and 6.2% Hispanic or Latino.<ref name="QuickFacts" />

